This paper is primarily focused on improving the efficiency of exploratory data analysis, which is a common task in database systems. Therefore, cs.DB (Database) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also introduces density maps and efficient algorithms, which are relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and data structures (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper mentions using techniques from the statistics literature, which could fall under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) or statistics (cs.ST).
